name: Brain Go:Tricky Test
description:
Start playing Brain Go today – a crazy puzzle game with a series of tricky brain teasers.
Lead the Brain Go Family to delight!

It's about time our brain test free mobile game with original ideas was given a chance.This creative and funny puzzle game may break common sense and bring your new brain-pushing experience!
Levels range from easy to hard for all adults to enjoy.Brain Go is your best choice to count your thumbs!

Features:
• Challenge your mind by answering fuuny riddles!
• Don't be mad when you get tricked!
• Train your problem solving ability!
• Massive creative Brain Teasers!
• Free to download!
• Suitable for all ages!
• The perfect trivia game for family & friends’ gatherings!
• Great time killer!
• Play without the internet!
